OL,7,FThe 23-year-old was serving in the
OL,8,FBritish Army when he started spying
OL,9,Ffor Iran and later escaped from
OL,10,FWandsworth prison on a food delivery
OL,11,Ftruck, ITV London's Political
OL,12,FCorrespondent Simon Harris reports
OL,14,FFormer soldier Daniel Khalife has been
OL,15,Fsentenced to 14 years and three months
OL,16,Ffor escaping from prison and spying
OL,17,Ffor Iran.
