OL,7,FKhalife, 23, escaped from HMP
OL,8,FWandsworth in September 2023, sparking
OL,9,Fnationwide attention, before he was
OL,10,Flater found to have shared sensitive
OL,11,Fmilitary information with Iran, which
OL,12,Fcould cause "serious harm."
OL,14,FPassing sentence at Woolwich Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Monday, Mrs Justice Cheema-
OL,16,FGrubb said he had been motivated by "a
OL,17,Fselfish desire to show off" and
OL,18,Fdescribed him as "a dangerous fool".
