OL,7,F"The mere fact that you started on
OL,8,Fthis dangerous and fantastical plan
OL,9,Fdemonstrates your immaturity and lack
OL,10,Fof wisdom, that you thought it was
OL,11,Fappropriate to insert yourself ` an
OL,12,Funauthorised, unqualified and
OL,13,Funinformed junior soldier into
OL,14,Fcommunication with an enemy state is
OL,15,Fperhaps the clearest indication of the
OL,16,Fdegree of folly in your failure to
OL,17,Funderstand at the most obvious level
OL,18,Fthe risk you posed," she said.
