OL,7,FOn top of his prison sentence, Khalife
OL,8,Fwas also ordered to pay #10,000
OL,9,Ftowards prosecution costs, which
OL,10,Ftotalled #134,000.
OL,12,FDefending Khalife, Gul Nawaz Hussain
OL,13,FKC compared Khalife's actions to "007
OL,14,Fand Scooby Doo".
OL,16,FHe told the court: "What Daniel
OL,17,FKhalife clearly chose to do was not
OL,18,Fborn of malice, was not born of greed,
OL,19,Freligious fervour or ideological
OL,20,Fconviction.
