OL,7,FPrison break
OL,9,FKhalife spent four days on the run
OL,10,Fafter using prison trousers to fasten
OL,11,Fhimself to a vehicle and escape
OL,12,Fcategory B prison, HMP Wandsworth, in
OL,13,Fsouth-west London.
OL,15,FHis escape launched one of the biggest
OL,16,Fmanhunts in recent years.
