OL,7,FHe gained national attention after
OL,8,Fbeing spotted buying clothes from
OL,9,FMarks & Spencer and a coffee from
OL,10,FMcDonald's in Richmond as well as
OL,11,Freading newspaper articles about
OL,12,Fhimself.
OL,14,FBefore he was caught, he attempted to
OL,15,Fcontact the Iranians, sending a
OL,16,FTelegram message which said simply: "I
OL,17,Fwait."
OL,19,FHe was caught on a canal towpath by a
OL,20,Fplainclothes detective days later.
