OL,12,FIn the trial, Khalife said he escaped
OL,13,Fin the hope he would be kept in a
OL,14,Fsegregated high-security unit at HMP
OL,15,FBelmarsh, away from "sex offenders"
OL,16,Fand "terrorists" after his recapture.
