OL,7,FKhalife joined the British Army in
OL,8,F2018, two weeks before his 17th
OL,9,Fbirthday, and served with the Royal
OL,10,FCorps of Signals.
OL,12,FWhile serving, Khalife gave Iran the
OL,13,Fnames of serving soldiers, including
OL,14,Fspecial forces personnel.
OL,16,FHe was paid in cash, some of which he
OL,17,Fforged, and told his handlers he
OL,18,Fplanned to stay in the military for
OL,19,Fover 25 years for them.
