OL,9,Fan internal spreadsheet of promotions
OL,10,Fin June 2021.
OL,12,FProsecutors believed he sent the list
OL,13,Fto Iran before deleting any evidence.
OL,15,FAfter his arrest, he told police he
OL,16,Fwished to offer himself to UK security
OL,17,Fagencies all along, having emailed MI6
