OL,7,FIn November 2021, he made an anonymous
OL,8,Fcall to the MI5 public reporting line,
OL,9,Fconfessing to having been in contact
OL,10,Fwith Iran for more than two years.
OL,12,FHe offered to help the British
OL,13,Fsecurity services and said he wanted
OL,14,Fto return to his normal life.
OL,16,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb told the
OL,17,Fcourt she did not believe Khalife had
OL,18,Fbeen honest about the full extent of
OL,19,Fthe information he had passed to Iran,
OL,20,Fkeeping only an incomplete record in
OL,21,Fcase he was caught.
