OL,7,FShe told Khalife during sentencing:
OL,8,F"When you joined the Army as a young
OL,9,Fman, you had the makings of an
OL,10,Fexemplary soldier.
OL,12,F"However, through the repeated
OL,13,Fviolation of your oath of service, you
OL,14,Fshowed yourself to be, instead, a
OL,15,Fdangerous fool."
OL,17,FIn November, jurors at Woolwich Crown
OL,18,FCourt found that Khalife had breached
OL,19,Fthe Official Secrets Act and the
OL,20,FTerrorism Act.
