OL,7,FHe was cleared of carrying out a bomb
OL,8,Fhoax at his Staffordshire barracks in
OL,9,FJanuary 2023 and had already admitted
OL,10,Fduring his trial to escaping from
OL,11,FWandsworth prison.
OL,13,FTwo men, Adeel Khan, 30, from Waltham
OL,14,FForest, and Imran Chowdhury, 25, from
OL,15,FChingford, east London, were also
OL,16,Fcharged in connection with helping
OL,17,FKhalife escape from prison.
